        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3276369475" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5751986536110727964">This book is so well-written. Each chapter jumps to two different eras, seemingly unconnected. The author then connects them. The author leaves the conclusion to the reader. That seemed like real life because people don&apos;t always know why things happen.</span>
  <span id="freeText5751986536110727964" style="display:none">This book is so well-written. Each chapter jumps to two different eras, seemingly unconnected. The author then connects them. The author leaves the conclusion to the reader. That seemed like real life because people don't always know why things happen.</span>
