<span id="freeTextContainer6366205620986425999">This novel was not as well crafted as &quot;Sold on a Monday&quot;. The transfers between time were not well transitioned. They felt choppy. That being said, the story was an interesting one.</span>
  <span id="freeText6366205620986425999" style="display:none">This novel was not as well crafted as "Sold on a Monday". The transfers between time were not well transitioned. They felt choppy. That being said, the story was an interesting one.</span>
